<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>@ViewBag.Title</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link href="@Url.Content("~/Content/Site.css")" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <script src="@Url.Content("~/Scripts/jquery-1.4.4.min.js")" type="text/javascript"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="wp">
        <div id="header">
            <p>
                建造中...运行于 Linux + ASP.NET 环境，尝鲜 MVC3 和 HTML5 技术。</p>
            <p>
                无心做兼容，推荐使用现代浏览器访问以得到最佳效果（<a href="http://www.mozilla.com/firefox/" target="_blank">Firefox
                    4.0</a>、<a href="http://www.google.com/chrome/" target="_blank">Chrome</a>、<a href="http://www.opera.com/"
                        target="_blank">Opera 11</a>、<a href="http://ie.microsoft.com/" target="_blank">IE9</a>等）</p>
            <div id="nav">
                <ul>
                    <li>@Html.ActionLink("首页", "Index", "Home")</li>
                    <li>@Html.ActionLink("关于", "About", "Home")</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div style="clear: both">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="main">
            @RenderBody()
        </div>
        <div id="footer">
            Powered by <span>WySky</span><br />
            Created @@2011
        </div>
        <div style="clear: both">
            <div id="toolbar">
                @if (Request.IsAuthenticated)
                {
                    <text>欢迎 @User.Identity.Name [@Html.ActionLink("退出", "LogOff", "Account")]</text>
                }
                else
                {
                    <text>点击 @Html.ActionLink("登录", "LogOn", "Account") 或 @Html.ActionLink("注册帐号", "Create", "Account")</text>
                }
                | 公告：网站玩耍中，大家请随意～
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- JiaThis Button BEGIN -->
        <script type="text/javascript">
            var jiathis_config = { "data_track_clickback": true };
        </script>
        <script type="text/javascript" src="http://v1.jiathis.com/code/jiathis_r.js?btn=r1.gif&amp;uid=889565"
            charset="utf-8"></script>
        <!-- JiaThis Button END -->
</body>
</html>
